# Desktop Shell
#
# The SimpleOS desktop environment built on the existing widget builder DSL.
# Provides a taskbar (window list, clock, system tray), an app launcher,
# and integration with the compositor for window management.
#
# The taskbar is itself a special compositor surface pinned to the bottom
# of the screen.

